# Standardized .gitignore: tailored to this repo's contents.

# ---- OS / editor cruft ----
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.idea/

# ---- Helm: vendored subcharts, archives, lockfiles (resolved in CI) ----
charts/
**/charts/
*.tgz
Chart.lock
**/Chart.lock
requirements.lock

# ---- AI / PR / review scratch: drafts that never belong in the repo ----
PR_*.md
PR_*.txt
PR_BODY*
REVIEW_CONSISTENCY*.md
*CONSISTENCY-REPORT*
migration.md
MIGRATION.md
RUN-TO-STRIP*.md
*_upstream_values.txt
.cruft.json
